A commercial bus driver in Lagos carried his protest a tad too far Wednesday when decided shoot shit at LASTMA officers trying to arrest him.
According to a video trending, the driver came out of the driver seat already occupied by an officer who ignored the driver’s threat to create a scene.
The protesting driver then put off his trousers, underwear, stooped, and shat in his own hand.
He then pasted the LASTMA officers with it.
Motorists have been frustrated by the extortion and harassment by the traffic management officers in the state, prompting aggression and scenarios like this across the state.
